Package: traveltimeR
Type: Package
Title: API Wrapper for the Traveltime Platform API 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: API Wrapper for the Traveltime Platform API (https://www.traveltimeplatform.com/).
How far can you travel from a certain location within a given timespan? Allows to get traveltime-isochrones for several transport-modes (public transport, car, bicycle, walking, driving & train) from the traveltime API. The isochrones come into R in form of geometries stored in sf-dataframes. 
API-Key required: (https://www.traveltimeplatform.com/)
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
